jzintvWii 1.0.1

This is a Wii port of jzintv Emulator, the multi-platform intellivision emulator created by Joe Zbiciak.

Please visit:
    http://spatula-city.org/~im14u2c/intv/


Please do NOT contact Joe Zbiciak for questions about jzintvWii, post them on the wiibrew page instead:
    http://wiibrew.org/wiki/Talk:JzintvWii
